{"tid":1869643,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"依家港獨聲音畀人騎劫， 引致美屬香港冇人聽到!「無政府狀態」陷入，應該宣稱喺美國領土!","createTime":"2020-02-08T09:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T13:49:44.000Z","uid":204929,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f029f725b3585082e0daa14ed0796b3398998da7","tid":1869643,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"究竟啲人有咩目的? 覺得創國好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?第一任總統?<br />\n如果要威嘅話做美國總統好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!包保世界個個都記得你， 而且你做得好嘅話對世界有貢獻， 大家都承認你啦!到時你講咩有大部分人認同! 如果做美國總統世界各地都為你歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />! 但香港總統， 只喺自己為內自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲出名嘅人(唔詳細講邊啲) 同埋部分網民, 係咪只係為咗自己利益， 而忽視大眾香港人利益， 所以就要香港獨立? 只係比親共派好嘅民主黨 擔心自己會畀右派嘅共和黨搶咗啲 議席?<br />\n我知都有啲唔係為自己利益， 我都想知點解?<br />\n<br />\n我明白，香港獨立， 嘅目的係脫離共匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但係真相係只有美屬香港 先至係真正脫離共匪! 因為你都唔夠共匪打!<br />\n<br />\n而且你代入共匪呢個角色， 你就知,一定會驚美屬好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 因為美軍可以極短時間攻打中共!但港軍, 就算全民皆兵， 都唔夠共匪打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n仲有， 你點樣可以確保 唔會畀共匪滲透? 一個小小嘅香港國, 唔使好耐，已經被滲透!<br />\n但美屬香港有美國保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香 港 已 經 陷 入 「無 政 府 狀 態」，短 期 內 將 成 立 香 港 臨 時 政 府 過 渡 委 員 會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1864675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1864675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解港獨會咁撚多?但美屬咁少人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n明明都有為數唔少嘅人提?"},{"pid":"4ba2a94735520050b347764448b87b3b06c5d2d9","tid":1869643,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2f48b25b7d7b2c5ad3be6ea211b9c00a22501b8","tid":1869643,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"俄屬安全d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53855217673c1ec1aae8575bdae2cd0f76fc6f0f","tid":1869643,"uid":246279,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:35:08.000Z","msg":"1. 點解美國會要你<br />\n<br />\n2. 你覺得美國好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做盟友ok<br />\nunder佢不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有香港人100%當家先係最好"},{"pid":"13db99b6ef8c11ddb1f456c418159532a02df06e","tid":1869643,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7f2a11c0923556189f7f0a68fca5b54f00a195d","tid":1869643,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:39:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"819fc2f6155f8a558eca465daf9a368dd3e159f6","tid":1869643,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18842608f74ccb116c35c7058a806857b99362bd","tid":1869643,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4d760568ae403a306eb46a766da956c78c5e16c","tid":1869643,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"13db99b6ef8c11ddb1f456c418159532a02df06e","tid":1869643,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">俄屬香港先係香港唯一出路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/apFKBPU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/apFKBPU</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俄軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor